        <abstract> 
<p>On <hi rend="italic">Vanilla</hi>.</p>  
<p>Asks JDH to observe whether he has both long- and short-styled form of <hi rend="italic">Menyanthes</hi></p> 
            <p>and whether he has "Saxifrages with long hairs glandular at the tip".</p>
            <p>The Linnean Society session made him vomit all night. Fears he must give up trying to read papers or speak. "It is a horrid bore. I can do nothing like other people."</p>
        </abstract>
